<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to zBox Labs, <%= @user.username %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully signed up to zBox Labs,
      your username is: <%= @user.email %>.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      The test we have prepared for you is as following: 
      <% @user.packages.each do |package| %>
      <%= "http://" + ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] + "/packages/#{package.id}" %>
      <% end %>
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and good luck!</p>
    </br>
    <p>Cheers,</p>
  </body>
</html>